snippet.title: PS4/PSV - Radio Hammer Station PV(English)
snippet.description:
From the 2D fighting game - "Chaos Code" team created the new Style Action Rhythm game - "Radio Hammer Station" will be available at 2017/11/1 (Asia region) for PlayStation(R)4 and PlayStation(R) Vita with Cross-buy!
